==German==
===Etymology===
Short for ''[[Untergrund]]-[[Bahn]]'' (underground railway). But note that the first German underground, in Berlin, was initally called an ''Unterpflaster-Bahn'' (underpavement railway).
===Noun===
'''U-Bahn''' ''f''

# An [[underground]] [[railway]].

